name: PHOTO - 2 "My Burden is LIGHT"
description:
by HP LoveBux

Street Scene in Boston MA

"Two paths cross, or do they?
the royal road, the ancient strength
the vision, the purpose, the poise.

Do you see me? - are we in one world?
or are our worlds in parallel apart?

Blessings up on you KING!
Your path and Your strength
speak louder than cities!

And I beheld you tread unheard useen
unstoppable as the centuries unnumbered."


 -- Sept. 2021 HPL
